ke up every morning legitimately believing that every opponent of Donald Tr=
ump is an existential threat to the country, and thus the ends justify the =
means.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:
0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;">Kash Patel literally wrote a book ab=
